    dc:description "FIGURES 9–12. Dexosarcophaga (Dexosarcophaga) campina sp. nov., male paratype, yellow pan trap, 6–14.vii. 2015 (MNRJ). 9. Epandrium, surstylus and cercus, left lateral view. 10. Gonites, left lateral view. 11. Distiphallus, ventral view. 12. Distiphallus, left lateral view. Abbreviations: jx = juxta; ls = lateral stylus; ms = median stylus; prg = pregonite; ptg = postgonite; ve = vesica. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2606513/files/figure.png" ;
